divs: Sighting Detailsnoticed a light rising above eastern horizon slowly moving west towards my location. Turned on my camera and pushed zoom button while watching the light to see if it flashed on and off like an airplane or helocopter. Light was constant so I snapped off a picture and it vanished prior to rising above my neighbors tree.
